      "storySummary": "STORY SO FAR: The party successfully defended themselves against rogue mercenaries in the Twilight Market, discovering a map to their hideout and a shimmering crystal that shattered, unveiling ominous runes. Grimoire Jones interacted with the remnants of the crystal, revealing warnings of a lurking threat associated with the mercenaries, heightening the tension in the air. Shadows flicker on the edges of their vision as they face cryptic messages and an impending danger, while Zulrokk restores their vigor with divine energy. \n\nCURRENT ARC: Mid escalation - The stakes are rising as the party must decode the warnings and prepare themselves for an impending confrontation with the rogue mercenaries.\n\nOPEN THREAD: The cryptic phrase revealed by the runes suggests a specific trait or secret of the rogue mercenaries that may provide insight into their motives or weaknesses.\n\nNEXT PROMISED BEAT: The party should collaboratively discuss and explore the runes further to unlock their mysteries, ideally revealing key information about the rogue mercenaries' next actions or their potential stronghold.\n\nRECENTLY RESOLVED: The encounter with the rogue mercenaries has concluded, leaving the party victorious and unharmed, setting the stage for new revelations.",
      "namespace_id": "local",
